<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Amic details capitalisation share award.</title>
<headline>Amic details capitalisation share award.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Anglo American Industrial Corp Ltd on Tuesday said it would offer capitalisation shares on the basis of the ratio that 410 cents bears to the average share price in the three days to April 30.</p>
<p>Registration for the issue is April 4.</p>
<p>Shareholders may elect to receive a final cash dividend of 385 cents per share for the year ended December 31, 1996 instead, the company said.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
